        "blueprint.json written at lock",
        "progress.md initialized at lock",
        "validate command presented",
        "status and follow commands presented",
        "single recommended launch command presented"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "harden-workshop",
      "prompt": "/run harden this thesis",
      "expected_nodes": [
        "nodes/harden.md",
        "nodes/blueprint-schema.md",
        "nodes/runner-handoff.md"
      ],
      "expected_output_shape": [
        "explicit hardening workshop separate from session",
        "thesis and proof bar reflected back clearly",
        "route to steelman when the seed is too foggy to state as a clear thesis",
        "bounded verify revise checklist proposed",
        "red-claim focus and stop rule made explicit",
